{
  "page": "Two Alans",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>two Alans</b> is the historical reference given to <a href=\"/index.php/Alan_Beesbury\" title=\"Alan Beesbury\">Alan Beesbury</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Alan_Tarly\" title=\"Alan Tarly\">Alan Tarly</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Honeyholt\" title=\"Lord of Honeyholt\">Lord of Honeyholt</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Horn_Hill\" title=\"Lord of Horn Hill\">Lord of Horn Hill</a> respectively, during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Two_Alans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The two Alans supported Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">blacks</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>. Together with Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Owen_Costayne\" title=\"Owen Costayne\">Owen Costayne</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Towers\" title=\"Three Towers\">Three Towers</a>, they harrassed the host of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Ormund_Hightower\" title=\"Ormund Hightower\">Ormund Hightower</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">greens</a> on his march north. Their actions culmulated in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Honeywine\" title=\"Battle of the Honeywine\">Battle of the Honeywine</a> where the two Alans were captured.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Two_Alans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - The Red Dragon and the Gold.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404225529\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.009 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.010 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 119/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8538/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 514/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 279/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 755/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    5.666      1 -total\n 77.95%    4.417      1 Template:Ref\n 49.17%    2.786      1 Template:Ref/core\n 20.86%    1.182      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:30535-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404225529 and revision i